creator: Thad Game
descriptionHtml:
Zombie Coloring is an art drawing game to color zombie theme artworks with color by numbers. A coloring book in the palm of your hand – open it and instantly forget your worries. Enjoy art, culture, freedom, and creativity, and unwind completely.

Creating a masterpiece is now as easy as one, two, three – all you need to do is match the colors according to the numbers and immerse yourself in a sea of self-expression. Unleash the artist within you! 

Key Features
- Simple & Easy to Paint Your Artworks
- Coloring Masterpieces Anytime & Anywhere, no pencil, paper needed.
- Quick sharing: post number coloring artworks on all social networks and share with friends and families.
